attacking ambitions in favor of a python-like squeeze on Black's miserable
pawns.} Nd5 16. Ne4 Rb8 (16... c4 $1 {is best, giving up a pawn for some play.}
) 17. Bg5 Qb6 18. c4 $1 Nf4 19. Be7 $1 Rf7 20. Bd6 $1 Rfb7 21. g3 (21. Nxe5 $1
$18) 21... Nxd3 22. Qe2 Nb4 23. a3 Nd5 24. cxd5 (24. Nxe5) 1-0

