1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 Nc6 3. Bb5 g6 4. Bxc6 bxc6 5. d3 Bg7 6. f4 d6 7. Nf3 Bg4 8. O-O
Nf6 9. Qe1 O-O 10. Qh4 Bxf3 11. Rxf3 e6 12. f5 Nd7 13. Bg5 $1 Bf6 14. Rh3 (14.
fxg6 fxg6 (14... Bxg5 15. Qxh7#) (14... hxg6 15. Rh3 $1 {With the h-file open,
this move is devastating.} Re8 16. Rf1 Kg7 17. Bxf6+ Qxf6 (17... Nxf6 18. Qh6+
Kg8 19. Qh8#) 18. Qh6+ Kg8 19. Rxf6 Nxf6 20. Qh8#) 15. Rxf6 Rxf6 (15... Nxf6
16. Rf1 Qb6 17. Bxf6 Qxb2 18. Nd5 $1 $18) 16. e5 dxe5 17. Ne4 Qb6 18. Bxf6 Nxf6
19. Nxf6+ Kg7 20. Qxh7+ Kxf6 21. Rf1+ Kg5 22. h4+ Kg4 23. Qxg6+ Kxh4 24. Kh2 $1
c4 25. g3#) 14... h5 15. Rg3 Kg7 16. Rf1 Rb8 17. Ne2 {Threatening Nf4xh5+ and
then Bxf6+, which would be devastating.} exf5 18. exf5 Bxg5 19. Rxg5 Kh6 20. f6
$1 Rb4 21. c4 Rxb2 22. Rxh5+ $1 gxh5 23. g4 (23. Ng3 {is even more brutal, but
who cares at this point?}) 1-0

