Ne5 d6 8. Nxc6 Nxc6 $11) 7. Nd2 (7. Ne5 {[%csl Rc4,Rc6,Rd3,Rf3,Rg4,Rg6]} d6 $19
) 7... Nf6 8. e3 O-O 9. Be2 c6 {[%cal Yd7d5]} 10. c5 d5 11. cxd6 Qxd6 12. Nc4
